arg(con8b).  % [con] Perfect clones would be treated in a different way than naturally born individuals.
arg(con24).  % [con] Cloning would lead to a lack of uniqueness.
arg(con24b).  % [con] Cloning would violate convictions regarding human individuality and freedom.

